</head>

<body>
    <h1>Privacy Policy for Café Aroma</h1>
    <p><strong>Effective Date: November 27, 2024</strong>
    </p>
    <p>At <strong>Café Aroma</strong>, your privacy is our priority. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use,
        and protect your personal information when you visit our website, use our services, or interact with us. By
        accessing our website, you agree to the
        practices described in this policy.</p>
    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect two main types of information:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> When you place an order, sign up for our
            newsletter, or create an account, we may collect your name, email address, shipping address, phone number,
            payment details, and any other information you provide.</li>
        <li><strong>Non-Personal Information:</strong> We may automatically gather data such as your IP address, browser
            type, device information, and pages visited on our website to improve your browsing experience.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>The information we collect is used to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Process and manage your orders.</li>
        <li>Provide customer support.</li>
        <li>Enhance our website, products, and services.</li>
        <li>Send promotions, updates, and newsletters (with your consent).</li>
        <li>Analyze website usage and improve user experience.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>3. Sharing Your Information</h2>
    <p>We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties, except in the following cases:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> We may share your information with trusted service providers (e.g.,
            payment processors, delivery companies) to help operate our website and
            fulfill your orders.</li>
        <li><strong>Legal Obligations:</strong> We may disclose your information to comply with legal requirements or
            respond to valid legal processes.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>4. Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use cookies to personalize your experience, analyze site traffic, and improve functionality.
        You can manage cookies through your browser settings, but disabling cookies may limit some website features.</p>
    <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
    <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access,
        loss, or misuse. However, no system is entirely secure, so please exercise caution when sharing sensitive
        information online.</p>
    <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access, update, or delete your personal information.</li>
        <li>Unsubscribe from promotional communications at any time.</li>
        <li>Request details about how your data is processed.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@cafearoma.com">privacy@cafearoma.com</a>.
    </p>
    <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. Any
        updates will be posted on this page with the new "Effective Date."</p>
    <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your personal information, feel free
        to reach out to us:</p>
    <p> <strong>Café Aroma</strong><br> Email: <a href="mailto:support@cafearoma.com">support@cafearoma.com</a>
        <br> Phone: +1 (555) 987-6543<br> Address: 456 Coffee Lane, AromaVille, CA 90210
    </p>
</body>

